comment: /**  * The SAML identifier (as a URI) for the IDP  */
code: /**  * The SAML identifier (as a URI) for the IDP  */ String getEntityId() {     return entityId. }

comment: /**  * A list of credentials that the IDP uses for signing messages.  * A trusted message should be signed with any one (or more) of these credentials.  */
code: /**  * A list of credentials that the IDP uses for signing messages.  * A trusted message should be signed with any one (or more) of these credentials.  */ List<Credential> getSigningCredentials() {     return signingCredentials.get(). }
